{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "14", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "44", "S": "22"}}, "news": [{"title": "NoBroker targets 30% revenue growth in FY27, eyes profitability in 12-15 months", "para": "NoBroker expects to grow revenue by about 30% in FY27 and become fully profitable in the next 12-15 months. The company said real estate continues to contribute about 50% of its revenue, while primary sales, NoBrokerHood, home services and packers & movers are supporting its broader ecosystem strategy.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/nobroker-aims-for-30-revenue-growth-and-profitability-in-next-15-months/132389389?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-562957/132389389.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "CBI files sixteenth chargesheet against Noida builder, bank officials", "para": "The CBI filed its sixteenth chargesheet concerning alleged large-scale homebuyers' fraud cases.  A Noida-based real estate company and bank officials face accusations of conspiracy.  These individuals allegedly cheated buyers and investors through fraudulent and deceptive means.  The investigation has unearthed substantial evidence of illegal activities and financial impropriety.  The agency continues to probe thirty-three other similar cases across the country.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/cbi-charges-noida-builder-and-bank-officials-in-massive-homebuyers-fraud-case/132390857?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-76986/132390857.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Beyond buildings: How architects are shaping sustainability and policy today", "para": "Architects now contribute significantly to India's development and urban planning.  Their inter